### 2. Vercel Deployment Configuration (`vercel.json`)
This file configures your Vercel deployment. It sets up the build environment and rewrites rules to expose your Phoenix Oracle as a serverless function.

```json
{
  "version": 2,
  "builds": [
    {
      "src": "package.json",
      "use": "@vercel/node",
      "config": {
        "includeFiles": ["dist/phoenix_oracle.js", "idl.json"]
      }
    },
    {
      "src": "next.config.js",
      "use": "@vercel/next"
    }
  ],
  "rewrites": [
    {
      "source": "/api/phoenix-oracle/:path*",
      "destination": "/api/phoenix_oracle"
    }
  ],
  "env": {
    "SOLANA_RPC_URL": "@next_public_solana_rpc_url",
    "PROGRAM_ID": "@next_public_solana_program_id"
  }
}
```

